strings: <voice_0x01001905><se_def>Dalmatian: It is an honor to dine with her majesty, and I have a secret to tell you.
<voice_0x01001907><se_low>King of tricks: What surprised me the most! Yes, it worked, you spend the night in the royal palace. Follow up as a reward for a job well done.
<voice_0x01001908><se_def>Dalmatian: Ha ha ha ha... Your Highness is very sweet.
